# Technical Requirements

- Core stack:
  - React 18+
  - TypeScript
  - Vite
  - Tailwind CSS
  - Framer Motion
  - Node.js v22+
  - Yarn v1.22+
- Build requirements:
  - Vite for dev/prod
  - Code splitting
  - Bundle analysis
  - Tree shaking
- Performance:
  - Route-based code splitting
  - Image optimization
  - Lazy loading
  - Bundle monitoring
- Security:
  - Helmet headers
  - CORS config
  - Env variables
  - Non-root Docker
  - CSP headers
- Debug features enabled:
  - Component debugging
  - Performance profiling
  - FPS monitoring
  - React DevTools